data.description: Welcome home to highly sought after Waterford Subdivision!  Centrally located on the edge of Daphne, you're just minutes from the interstate and Alabama's Gulf Coast!  This truly custom craftsman boasts so many upgrades.  Scored and stained concrete floors on the lower level, stone counters throughout, custom trim package, cozy wood burning fire place, stainless appliances, custom chefs kitchen, wrap around front porch, MASSIVE 15 X 22 bonus room, screened in back patio, and the list goes on!  This home has been meticulously maintained and is ready for its new owners.  Call your favorite agent today for your private tour!
